{"tid":305260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎扁桃腺發炎","createTime":"2017-07-01T13:49:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T13:55:17.000Z","uid":104903,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4668d604bebdd92f36c2d554472a58b3c70f2635","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺發炎真係令人好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我間唔中就會發炎 好辛苦<br />\n我淨係知道飲多d水會有d用<br />\n其實都唔知係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇醫生要食兩三個抗生素療程先開始好<br />\n又食唔到野講野又痛 嚴重上黎乜都唔做都好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都有經驗<br />\n認真post 只係想快d好番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17623037f3272de86f57b9d8762a0e72f43378f","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"自push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2686e3c6550e8eb0fc58fbe1060bad1fb163f3f7","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:50:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"fc362c9a703fb12e7bdf711d1a972549352a2354","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"次次都要幾個星期先好得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b812b87fdb285a362ac4cdb0b520f8744adca442","tid":305260,"uid":15031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9ace142c6817d010b5785ec32bbcde5c07610fc","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"聽講可以切除扁桃腺 但免疫力會變到好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d988334dccc7b161189fd8d730148d5061a7f","tid":305260,"uid":15031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5144b58d7fcc8b2c6c4348f65acac1d2c37e2ebd","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次都要幾個星期先好得番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n醫生救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f477791218de93ce435c7cc7a590181d8506eab","tid":305260,"uid":104903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友有做扁桃體切除手術 好似幾work</blockquote><br />\n有無詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我聽講免疫力會差好多 都一樣會有其他病痛<br />\n自己本身已經係潺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9176d904ac781b8920da7cab637bcf108eb49f7","tid":305260,"uid":15031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"56b2111816205048332c539f99b3a425936ac3dc","tid":305260,"uid":4536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"發緊炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4020e6ca514ec507883b71300dee2134c651fc","tid":305260,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"成日都會 究竟做乜先會發炎"},{"pid":"be066416befd3f7a36c30bbe9e02cd7aadfb572f","tid":305260,"uid":56775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩好返兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bb3667a4aaf39a51ca08a2aaf8fc5285fc8310","tid":305260,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朋友有做扁桃體切除手術 好似幾work</blockquote><br />\n有無詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我聽講免疫力會差好多 都一樣會有其他病痛<br />\n自己本身已經係潺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問醫生啦<br />\n真係有得切"},{"pid":"a81d2f9d5f38bf9de5565be0ce9c19b47fabc15f","tid":305260,"uid":6034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"我扁桃腺之前成日都發炎<br />\n之後入仁安切左扁桃腺<br />\n埋單3定4萬<br />\n之後就好少好少喉嚨痛"},{"pid":"f3684d889d2c246e8c80a7953e7d0b484c52efa3","tid":305260,"uid":7488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:17:04.000Z","msg":"得閒含下白醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對身體幾好"},{"pid":"0758962917cb17701e502984b20467e07e753209","tid":305260,"uid":770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"我都發緊炎。。<br />\n我每隔兩三個月就會發炎一次<br />\n成日食抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b20fca70783da4f00dc113db637faabcfa6597d","tid":305260,"uid":77371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"有 第一次發炎係小學三年級 <br />\n嗰年病到入院<br />\n住左差唔多一個星期<br />\n日日都痛到食唔到野咁濟<br />\n唯獨是食啲凍嘢先舒服啲<br />\n醫生都畀我食雪糕<br />\n一吞口水就痛到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔吞嘢嗰時就耳仔痛<br />\n淨係耳仔痛都痛到瞓唔著<br />\n差唔多每晚都要叫姑娘塞止痛藥落patpat（雖然我唔知點解塞嗰度）<br />\n瞓著之後又超大鼻鼾聲<br />\n因為扁桃體腫到阻住我呼吸<br />\n嘈到我阿媽都瞓唔到<br />\n之後時不時到宜家20歲都會病發<br />\n但就無細個咁嚴重<br />\n每次都係靠食抗生素好返"},{"pid":"38743deffe5ed7a5aa61294a2cdbd93ff1410738","tid":305260,"uid":76958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"扁桃線發炎真係好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4894d49986f41e592cb55503b23c538fa8e9cc","tid":305260,"uid":101693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6b546bb36cb2fc9a6d6d6ec0f45e1950fbd395","tid":305260,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"要好小心留意<br />\n屋企人以前又係成日發炎<br />\n唔知有冇關係得出個扁桃腺癌<br />\n小心飲食咪食咁多熱氣野啦"},{"pid":"5390a05bbe543b7d5abfa984e3aa9aade332fe79","tid":305260,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"吞口水痛，持續發燒，個喉嚨有d白色野，係咪即係扁桃腺發炎？我斷斷續續幾日都退唔到燒，之前睇醫生佢仲比d咳水，喉糖我，完全冇效"},{"pid":"e00d9287b90179dd0afa1592e14fdbfa0b1b06b2","tid":305260,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"好辛苦，食完退燒藥好少少，之後又發熱"},{"pid":"a7fa0e81943db76dbf9af3bede25a33d5dcdcd67","tid":305260,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"太密的話切吧"},{"pid":"ca23096b4e288b44ab00489a984e70aa0c1621ff","tid":305260,"uid":73082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:25:50.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺發炎中 同感"},{"pid":"9bebb96596b088cdd329b4b68fcccf5fc6ec29af","tid":305260,"uid":58618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"半年左右就發一次 每次通常都2個星期好<br />\n你幾星期有啲耐 真係要逼自己飲水 用飲筒飲咩都好"},{"pid":"11c984cddce9d556234e62694f965cc207334163","tid":305260,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吞口水痛，持續發燒，個喉嚨有d白色野，係咪即係扁桃腺發炎？我斷斷續續幾日都退唔到燒，之前睇醫生佢仲比d咳水，喉糖我，完全冇效</blockquote><br />\n要食抗生素同消炎藥架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b337347773e04b15c0692c371371ac5d71c90a62","tid":305260,"uid":45350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"用口呼吸？"},{"pid":"3bf5d2ba9add010546d9539b908c24fea90238bd","tid":305260,"uid":125687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:35:53.000Z","msg":"我都係 經常發發下炎開始發燒<br />\n都試過兩次啱好需要講嘢 講多幾句 第二日失聲"},{"pid":"5be0c79115c4c5e9180646c91e6e01729ff6c5ea","tid":305260,"uid":75154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T15:36:14.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁 近兩年都無發炎<br />\n飲水真係work"},{"pid":"888b9e82b2d0248e97f2a175b4b9cf3446c688fb","tid":305260,"uid":103342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"我都做左切扁桃腺 唔知點解切完之後<br />\n口腔上顎位置間唔中起粒粒 過一二日<br />\n又無左 唔知有冇巴絲打有同樣經驗<br />\nps 問過醫生 醫生話可能同防腐劑<br />\n食物有關 唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8979b6064ef0d19b90041ef8c797c84208dad5","tid":305260,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都做左切扁桃腺 唔知點解切完之後<br />\n口腔上顎位置間唔中起粒粒 過一二日<br />\n又無左 唔知有冇巴絲打有同樣經驗<br />\nps 問過醫生 醫生話可能同防腐劑<br />\n食物有關 唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又無事喎"},{"pid":"76f215cb95ff6b6c27f7b8acab75655fbd195198","tid":305260,"uid":45992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:54:29.000Z","msg":"早排先發完炎 痛撚到吞口水都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c2e232493097e0021b762025c20996adc7bd74","tid":305260,"uid":51774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:14:08.000Z","msg":"唔知關唔關我媽遺傳事<br />\n佢以前又係成日發炎 最後切左<br />\n我多數黎m前 抵抗力差少少 或者 果排食得多熱氣野 辣野 就會黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我媽叫我少食辣加多飲水 依家就好似好番啲咁<br />\n無咁易發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但次次發炎 都一樣痛幾星期 要食兩 三個抗生素療程先會好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次最勁睇第四次醫生 話我今次仲唔好 就要做手術切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嚇死我 好彩最後好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bb788dac6cb38c156ca1da613bc631906574e8","tid":305260,"uid":1510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:22:23.000Z","msg":"細個要食兩三個月抗生素 食菠蘿都發炎 之後醫生話係扁桃腺增生 做埋個睡眠窒息測試 就決定切 而家好少發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又無咩點病"},{"pid":"02c422c5166972b1212a5a3fe44bf444895080be","tid":305260,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:29:01.000Z","msg":"琴日先切完 私家醫院切 睇醫生到約手術 完成埋都唔洗十日 4萬蚊內<br />\n切完之後己經3日食粥水 要係咁食抗生素 止痛藥<br />\n我反覆性扁桃腺發炎比較勁 平均一個月一次 一次要最小十日先好返 其間係咁發高燒 前前後後病左成年幾 真係頂唔順先切 希望切完真係可以還我健康啦"},{"pid":"fca95cef2fc65dad35a9afc8fac208e369c7586d","tid":305260,"uid":92582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"以前小學有過幾次，痛到喊又排過急症(因為咳到痰已經有血)，如果睇醫生一定要佢開消炎藥同抗生素， 有隻消炎藥係白色藥水， 好結， 嗰隻勁有效， 因為試過唔同醫生講到好嚴重， 醫生就咁開止痛藥 同消炎藥 ，係完全冇效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c487713c2c090a18f8d4f1fead64548b40235c","tid":305260,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"智慧齒？"},{"pid":"eb9e90bbfdb0c9092894fe3edfdbdb204bdb25c2","tid":305260,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"我由中學開始，凍親之後就會好容易發炎，近排就極少發炎，近幾年一年一次左右<br />\n<br />\n之後幾日都要著多啲衫、一發現出汗立即抹左佢、飲多啲水、一急屎要立即痾<br />\n<br />\n好多時併發發燒、咳、出黃痰，食啲牛黃解毒片快則一日、慢則五日完全好返"},{"pid":"7d61447160e77cd6ea48bd883d68a21ca1ca28b7","tid":305260,"uid":92592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好辛苦，食完退燒藥好少少，之後又發熱</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4289a75456dd774b207642bb7d89272e2d967f33","tid":305260,"uid":107288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"有時會有白色珍珠 同個坑好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n切左扁脁腺解唔解決到？"},{"pid":"ca9a1a0b97e912b3f57494c7012e8d6a611248e6","tid":305260,"uid":86072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 切左之後好少病"},{"pid":"9a287c024856be28d00ffdf66a3019d369ae8091","tid":305260,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1df1f7986ea566fd06e0b700247dccfead4a103","tid":305260,"uid":28328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"切左佢啦<br />\n我再發多次就去切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53a72ee3acb65e4b600f94c5f839daaa1fe734e","tid":305260,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:53:40.000Z","msg":"我病左4日，係咪喉嚨果d白色野唔退，仲會繼續發燒？<br />\n連續3日朝早都燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f0954e8eac14e696d5cdcedcd753e74e9dce9f","tid":305260,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"用漱口水浪到喉嚨位會無咁易發炎"},{"pid":"3853db11d230a3671038028220d113b6bcac15f5","tid":305260,"uid":54834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"之前會厭潰瘍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 威力拍得住扁腺線發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食物飲水生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478bb5cfa9db88b4555afe50d5fcf63ce0296405","tid":305260,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"受害者"},{"pid":"3f4c7dc12ecaf91be0305fc69721f7a3b579fba2","tid":305260,"uid":92126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"細個都成日發炎 跟著中醫西醫都叫我切左佢<br />\n切左之後冇乜影響 好似仲病少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b81f47fa93cec822a825f4f2a4bcbe970222a9","tid":305260,"uid":15866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小妹都發緊炎 發咗5日唔係好對路 睇埋急症而家住埋院<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為吞咗啲膿落胃搞到有併發症 食乜嘔乜 共勉之啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}